    {
      "title": "The Long Night",
      "lines": [
        "Fog rolls off the black water and the cluster camp douses its lights.",
        "Three relay pylons stand cold in the reeds — north, west, south.",
        "The peat seeps poison and the Entropy wades the channels. Hold the ring. Sortie between waves."
      ],
