  "npcs": [
    {
      "id": "warden-okafor",
      "name": "Warden Okafor",
      "lines": [
        "Nightwave's close — walls up, lights low. The fog hides them till they're on the wire.",
        "In this dark they see eight tiles, no further. Stay dim, strike first.",
        "Five gaps in my barricade ring, frames already stood. Mind the lane gaps.",
        "The pylons sit out in the black — north, west, south. Sortie between waves, never during.",
        "Watch the peat — it weeps poison. And the toads spit it onto the causeways. Don't dawdle on a bridge."
      ],
      "gift": {
        "shards": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "doc-aroyo",
      "name": "Doc Aroyo",
      "lines": [
        "You again! Last needle I put in you was at the Crossing keep. Small frontier.",
        "Hm, hm-hmm... the old transit jingle. Pre-Fall. It keeps my hands steady.",
        "Crystal nodes glow along the causeways — four shards a node. Crack them before the waves trample through.",
        "Stay by the braziers between sorties. This cold fog gets into the joints.",
        "When the relays settle, the lines run again. I'll hum us the whole way home."
      ]
    }
  ],
